column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "91EC71C7407316D43FE32CA63E807ADD", "Welcome young man.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "DEC1D7B74DE1E703580867BE6E797116", "You\'re Cherrymon, right?")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "FC340EFC4F286E4D4F1D67B57C60B7DF", "What do you want with an old man like me?")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "F4EAFE9248E66D08525D8C86309A2D3C", "First, clear the fog.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "0EFD74C447FA9098500B3B9E5FC7D8E1", "I can\'t see with the fog. Can you get rid of it?")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "148D2E8447E2C1C020F164AFCF2DF702", "So, that\'s it. I see.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "C3DD2FAF4FD6F9CF16FC9EAD55AB6D14", ".. can\'t you do it?")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "10CB44A74C016E90F5A8E08DB04694C9", "First, listen to what I got to say. Now... where should I begin?")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "F3A4A1564F167B3C58294C83E15C2321", "If you know about the emergency on the island, please tell me about it.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "C36EEDE648180F61C07A2A9AC740EC57", "I see, I see. The emergency.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "572F1DE94829587A50F90298E23AC6AE", "This island began to change eighty years ago after the land changes happened.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "9048A22A4C10E17A00121D83E7DD3CEE", "The northeastern parts of the island suddenly appeared eighty years ago.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "BD645B87408CBBC2A545E8A282CBC3FB", "Since then, Digimon started to move away. The species separated.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "78CD0B8F45A1F675C304B2840C3DB4D4", "And each species started to speak their own tongue.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "6DD48C2C4E829CCC8117E391AD64D6D6", "They forgot the language they used in the city...")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "FAC578494E06B6A6850718960CF3B58A", "In the end, File City lost most of its population of Digimon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "9D9FAE2A458B728963249786170240DF", "Then Digimon began to lose their memory!")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "541B036F40829434B098938CE4E2C78F", "The island\'s history, their past, their senses... getting worse day by day.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "4C6702AD466B7CF1378F7FABB715B0B3", "But I have something important to tell you, but I can\'t remember it, either.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "944DE2A641B311A8FFDF40B8FEF275C5", "However, all will come together in the end. Someone compels it to be so!")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "7193745741063BCA418AC19FA614A2E9", "In time, the Digimon will come to think of the emergency as normal.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "C61D610B429ACF9BECD4A48420428997", "The only thing that can stop this is you and the power of File City to unify Digimon!")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "2F0EB85640036CA6770B4DBD669B5108", "Gather Digimon in the city and create a miracle. It will definitely happen.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "73ED5918497AAE975772769C9A67A03F", "Well, I got all worked up. Phew, I\'ve said it all.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "EE0267D64885EB64B1321195AEC355AC", "Now, let\'s get rid of the fog.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "11E249F649833C24C1CCECAF467BD5EC", "The reason for the forest fog was to be able to speak to you. Oh, one more thing...")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "DC33A63E433C7BD45CE08C93518F8157", "There are others in the forest who know about the past.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "6F990E52430682D97558D8A68092003E", "Go deep into the forest to find them, if you can.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "81E1E4D648004AD3106241BA1F6AAB09", "Did you come here again to hear an old man talk?")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "B75ED55E4BDEEDE0A9FC41AD9DDEC61D", "Here\'s what I have to say.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4B937254D3327FAE81BD0B52A6F5B43]", "024E75A9452B62E90CAC05AF1BDA7FC8", "Ha ha ha.")
